content.text:
I don't have any memory of previous conversations. Each conversation with me starts fresh - I don't have access to chat history or any code you may have asked me to remember in past sessions.

However, if you have code you'd like me to work with in *this* conversation, feel free to share it! I can help you:
- Write new code
- Debug existing code
- Explain code
- Refactor or optimize code
- Test code using the bash tool

Just paste or describe the code you'd like to work on, and I'll be happy to help!
